def descriere_ananas():
	return "The pineapple (Ananas comosus) is a tropical plant with an edible fruit. In the wild, pineapples are pollinated primarily by hummingbirds.[2][7] Certain wild pineapples are foraged and pollinated at night by bats. The introduction of the pineapple plant to Europe in the 17th century made it a significant cultural icon of luxury."